name: XTZ O.F.
description: One day, when the world runs on Tezos, you'll find yourself interviewing for an Amazon Corporate Citizenship. You've only ever flipped NFTs for income and have no real skill set, so in a desperate bid to impress your betters, you'll claim that you were a Tezos early adopter. While all your peers were fisting themselves to see who could pay more in Ethereum fees, you saw the big picture. Skeptically, they'll look at you and ask one simple question "how many fukrs do you own?" You'll feel your ass clap shut with an audible report as you realize you've just been called out.  You own none. YOU. ARE. A. FRAUD.  No TeZOs TiLl wE BeZoS jokes are gonna pull you out of this nose dive...unless of course, you own yourself one of these.  Stop seeking validation from the XTZ elite! This NFT is your proof to the world that you ARE a XTZ Original Fukr! This sleek lizard boi is so close to the original thing, nobody will be able to tell the difference. Seize the means of recognition and legitimacy today!
